						               													<description>This is a card game play in turns.  In a turn, each player play a card from hand to the 4 row of the card.  When a sixth card play to the row, the player who play the sixth card get the first to fifth cards (5 cards) and the sixth card become the new first card of the row.  The sum of the victory points (VP) on the 5 cards is the VP for the player.  Different cards have different VP value, some positive and some negative.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are rules to play the card, only higher number card may be place to the cards on the table.  If no card can be place, the longest row on the mat will be discard and replace with a new card from the deck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play continue until all players play all the cards in the hand (10 cards).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The one with the most VP win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Component:&amp;#10;80 cards with number from 1 to 80&amp;#10;7 special card (same card back as the number card)&amp;#10;1 rule sheet&amp;#10;1 play mat&amp;#10;A small game box&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
